        <div id="recentposts-2" class="module nocontent widget_recentposts"><h4 class="moduleHeader">Recent Posts</h4>				<div class="entry">
						<div class="w50 right">
				<a href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/12/05/after-nine-years-and-2810-posts-a-dot-earth-farewell/"><img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2012/10/23/blogs/dotearthmaprace/dotearthmaprace-thumbStandard-v2.jpg" width="50" height="50" /></a>
			</div>
							<h6 class="kicker">
					<a href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/category/sustainability/">sustainability</a>
				</h6>
							<h5><a href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/12/05/after-nine-years-and-2810-posts-a-dot-earth-farewell/" title="Read: After Nine Years and 2,810 Posts, a Dot Earth Farewell">After Nine Years and 2,810 Posts, a Dot Earth Farewell</a>
			<span class="postMetaHeaderCommentCount commentCount hidden">
					<i class="icon"></i>
					<a class="commentCountLink commentCountNumberOnly commentCountNoPrompt" href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/12/05/after-nine-years-and-2810-posts-a-dot-earth-farewell/"></a>
				</span>			</h5>
			<p class="summary">
